{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/LEET/L2182ConstructStringWithRepeatLimit/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"2182. Construct String With Repeat Limit","date":"December 17, 2024"},"html":"<h1>문제 설명</h1>\n<p>이 문제는 문자열 <code>s</code>와 정수 <code>repeatLimit</code>가 주어지면, <code>s</code>의 문자를 <code>repeatLimit</code>만큼 반복하여 만들 수 있는 가장 긴 lexicographic 문자열을 만드는 문제이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 114.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2182\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f154b2a21fbbe3dcaaaa713622517063/5a190/2182.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f154b2a21fbbe3dcaaaa713622517063/772e8/2182.png 200w,\n/static/f154b2a21fbbe3dcaaaa713622517063/e17e5/2182.png 400w,\n/static/f154b2a21fbbe3dcaaaa713622517063/5a190/2182.png 800w,\n/static/f154b2a21fbbe3dcaaaa713622517063/d53ff/2182.png 1068w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>풀이 및 해설</h2>\n<p>크게는 다음 흐름을 따라갔습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>while more than two characters have counts larger than 1</li>\n<li>use as many large characters as possible (up to repeatLimit)</li>\n<li>append them to a string</li>\n<li>remove the added count to the counter</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>풀이</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">from collections import Counter\n\nclass Solution:\n    def repeatLimitedString(self, s: str, repeatLimit: int) -> str:\n        pq = [(-ord(char), cnt) for char,cnt in Counter(s).items()]\n        heapify(pq)\n        print(pq)\n\n        result = []\n\n        while pq:\n            char, cnt = heappop(pq)\n            if result and result[-1] == char:\n                if not pq: break\n                next_char,next_cnt = heappop(pq)\n                result.append(next_char)\n                if next_cnt-1: heappush(pq, (next_char, next_cnt-1))\n                heappush(pq, (char, cnt))\n            else:\n                m = min(cnt, repeatLimit)\n                result.extend([char] * m)\n                if cnt-m: heappush(pq, (char, cnt-m))\n        return ''.join(chr(-x) for x in result)\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Complexity Analysis</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"tc\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/24ddb792abd08ca4b285fb46581db12d/5a190/tc.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/24ddb792abd08ca4b285fb46581db12d/772e8/tc.png 200w,\n/static/24ddb792abd08ca4b285fb46581db12d/e17e5/tc.png 400w,\n/static/24ddb792abd08ca4b285fb46581db12d/5a190/tc.png 800w,\n/static/24ddb792abd08ca4b285fb46581db12d/97bfd/tc.png 1078w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>시간 복잡도</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Counter: O(n)</li>\n<li>pq: O(klogk)</li>\n<li>while loop: O(n)</li>\n<li>pop and push: O(logk)</li>\n<li>Total: O(nlogk)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>공간 복잡도</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>O(n+k)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Constraint Analysis</h2>\n<pre><code>Constraints:\n1 &#x3C;= repeatLimit &#x3C;= s.length &#x3C;= 10^5\ns consists of lowercase English letters.\n</code></pre>\n<h1>References</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/construct-string-with-repeat-limit/\">2182. Construct String With Repeat Limit</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/LEET/L2182ConstructStringWithRepeatLimit/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}